7 427   Edm. Thou, Nature, art my goddess; to thy law
7 428      My services are bound. Wherefore should I
7 429      Stand in the plague of custom, and permit
7 430      The curiosity of nations to deprive me,
7 431      For that I am some twelve or fourteen moonshines
7 432      Lag of a brother? Why bastard? wherefore base?
